Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.16,0:01:50.56,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰かを悲しませてまで　笑えなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.71,0:02:01.31,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そう言って彼女はうつむいてたんだ　夜に泣いた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.04,0:02:08.90,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷たく貼り付いて　凍えている
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.10,0:02:15.86,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降り続く現実に　傘などない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.44,0:02:22.60,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生きてゆくことが　戦いなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.71,0:02:26.33,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そんな理由だけで　閉じ込められた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.43,0:02:29.22,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My Heart　My Story
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.38,0:02:36.71,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泪のムコウが見えるの　輝いている
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.92,0:02:43.41,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小さな窓には　あの頃みたいに　青い空が映る
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.68,0:02:50.16,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ah  ah　鳥のように　飛べはしないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.18,0:03:01.64,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰かを悲しませたとき　感じる痛み
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.77,0:03:03.42,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘れないように
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.54,0:03:09.00,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そっと目を閉じて　泣いた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.16,0:01:50.56,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在傷害別人之前　不必強顏歡笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.71,0:02:01.31,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說著她低下頭　在黑夜裡哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.04,0:02:08.90,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰冷黏合在一起　渾身僵硬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.10,0:02:15.86,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨下個不停　卻沒有傘來遮擋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.44,0:02:22.60,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把自己囚禁在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.71,0:02:26.33,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有戰鬥才能求生的因果之中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.43,0:02:29.22,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心　我的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.38,0:02:36.71,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淚水的彼岸所見到的　是五彩光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.92,0:02:43.41,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小的窗口　映照出那時蔚藍的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.68,0:02:50.16,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　雖說不能像鳥兒一樣自由翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.18,0:03:01.64,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷害別人之後的那份心痛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.77,0:03:03.42,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不忘卻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.54,0:03:09.00,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕輕地閉上眼　哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.11,0:03:21.61,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}#23  生命之花
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.25,0:00:29.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來  伊奧利亞計劃的一切都變成我的了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.48,0:00:31.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太傲慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.61,0:00:48.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…  怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.21,0:00:53.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為…  為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.81,0:00:57.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的意識是直接與吠陀連接在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.25,0:01:00.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉體不過是一個容器而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.00,0:01:02.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.99,0:01:06.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做不到的事  我能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.48,0:01:11.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我應該說過的  我是你們的上位者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.86,0:01:13.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,李本茲——！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.04,0:01:31.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大將  A-LAWS那邊好像不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.10,0:01:34.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是該我出場了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.08,0:01:37.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待你的表現
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.27,0:03:28.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校  A-LAWS的旗艦被擊沉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.85,0:03:31.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  把敵艦隊分割開
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.61,0:03:34.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS隊  集中攻擊艦隊中央！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.42,0:03:36.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.05,0:03:39.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上  上校！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.72,0:03:50.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.06,0:04:04.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了  Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.80,0:04:07.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正規軍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.17,0:04:09.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那  敵艦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.84,0:04:31.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別節省彈藥！  跟著聯邦軍前進！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.29,0:04:46.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改革者不在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.50,0:04:48.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易斯呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.70,0:04:52.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵艦隊被分割成了兩半
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.53,0:04:55.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種戰術…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.33,0:05:01.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊恩  集中攻擊正面中央的艦隊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.75,0:05:02.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開一個突破口！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.20,0:05:05.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白  琳達！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.48,0:05:06.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.34,0:05:30.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣突破艦隊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.12,0:05:33.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam請專心保護母艦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.13,0:05:39.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重複  Gundam請專心保護母艦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.23,0:05:40.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.13,0:05:42.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦軍發來的通信？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.07,0:05:44.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是馬內金
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.19,0:05:47.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了  九條
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.64,0:05:50.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡蒂·馬內金…  為什麼你會…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.83,0:05:52.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.85,0:05:57.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只是為了給A-LAWS斷罪而利用你們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.28,0:06:03.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等這場戰鬥結束後再找你們問罪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.15,0:06:05.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡蒂…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.85,0:06:08.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通知所有部隊！ 立即進行回避動作！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.65,0:06:10.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了！  攻擊來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.31,0:06:12.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不祥的光線！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.15,0:06:23.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後方出現強烈能源反應！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.83,0:07:15.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.07,0:07:19.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.93,0:07:35.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改革者！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.53,0:07:43.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥停止了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.25,0:07:47.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  剛才那巨大的光線是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.61,0:07:49.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.76,0:07:59.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始準備第二次掃射
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.19,0:08:03.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白  開始進行GN-Drive的更換作業
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.21,0:08:22.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光學迷彩解除
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.45,0:08:26.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各自報告受損情況
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.05,0:08:29.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密  右舷損傷輕微
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.17,0:08:32.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡塔隆  運輸艦1艘被擊沉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.70,0:08:35.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS好像也有20台以上受到重創
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.65,0:08:38.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS艦隊已開始撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.85,0:08:42.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.44,0:08:42.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.46,0:08:44.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顯示到屏幕上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.76,0:08:50.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…  那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.36,0:09:25.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是…  那些傢伙的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.23,0:09:32.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殖民地型外太空航行母艦  Celestial Being
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.48,0:09:39.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奧利亞在2個世紀以前就預見到與未知種族的遭遇…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.59,0:09:41.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,及即將到來的對話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.06,0:09:45.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN-Drive  吠陀  改革者…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.47,0:09:47.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.52,0:09:51.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這艘船才是人類的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.52,0:09:57.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將人類從滅亡中拯救出來…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.97,0:10:03.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是所謂的「方舟」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.71,0:10:12.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通知各艦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.05,0:10:18.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們Celestial Being接下來將開始對敵方大型母艦的進攻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.95,0:10:24.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並進行將那裡的量子型演算系統——吠陀奪回的作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.92,0:10:30.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡對一直幫助我們到現在的各位表示感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.25,0:10:34.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並對戰死的人們表示哀悼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.56,0:10:36.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麗莎…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.08,0:10:40.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉塞  把托勒密的航向調整為敵方母艦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.99,0:10:43.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白  把航向修正為敵方母艦！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.71,0:10:58.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧  開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.31,0:11:00.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奪回吠陀！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.79,0:11:03.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最壞的情況  即使將其破壞也要阻止敵母艦的行動！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.38,0:11:07.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了即將到來的未來…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.69,0:11:19.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  走吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.63,0:11:23.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為我們之前改變世界的補償
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.94,0:11:25.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做個了斷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.50,0:11:29.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把世界從改革者的支配下解放出來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.88,0:11:31.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次改變世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.58,0:11:33.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了未來！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.29,0:11:38.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN Field  最大展開！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.18,0:11:45.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Last mission  Start！{\r}\N最後的任務  開始！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===================================
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.94,0:11:58.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本艦在探索入侵路線的同時前進
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.13,0:12:02.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各Gundam攻擊炮台以確保進攻路線
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.41,0:12:03.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.19,0:12:04.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.27,0:12:07.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解  打開進攻路線
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.93,0:12:08.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.56,0:12:36.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大型炮台鎖定這邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.74,0:12:37.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉塞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.42,0:12:38.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.22,0:12:56.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒完沒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.67,0:13:00.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.68,0:13:03.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克恩！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.62,0:13:04.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特瑞亞！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.07,0:13:06.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過如此！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.69,0:13:30.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得還不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.41,0:13:33.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒到我們出場嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.18,0:13:35.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有Gaga部隊就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.18,0:13:35.74,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（Gaga：改革者量產型MS，和Gadessa、Garazzo一樣\N都是Ga打頭，駕駛員為克隆人）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.24,0:13:39.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們就留到關鍵時刻吧  希琳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.15,0:13:40.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.80,0:13:49.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在進攻路線上的敵粒子炮已排除57%了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.94,0:13:52.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有新的MS部隊來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.23,0:14:03.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是新型機嗎！ 而且數量還這麼多！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.94,0:14:06.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那形狀…難道是！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.95,0:14:14.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們就被自己的技術毀滅吧  Celestial Being
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.22,0:14:16.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.30,0:14:19.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM……
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.49,0:14:24.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然是TRANS-AM？！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.62,0:14:26.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這數量！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.70,0:14:28.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.74,0:14:29.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們迎擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.29,0:14:43.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人的MS徑直朝我們衝來！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.68,0:14:47.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是特攻兵器！ 將炮擊集中在右舷！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.96,0:15:03.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普特利麥奧斯被…！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.73,0:15:10.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.88,0:15:15.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎  怎麼會！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.64,0:15:16.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.63,0:15:50.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特  找到入侵點了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.46,0:15:51.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.56,0:16:02.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.50,0:16:14.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使要將本艦當作盾也要守住！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.55,0:16:15.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不能讓他們被擊沉！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.39,0:16:18.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡塔隆！ 卡蒂！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.85,0:16:20.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼  九條！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.98,0:16:22.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快繼續執行任務！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.95,0:16:23.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡蒂…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.99,0:16:26.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右舷後方有敵機！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.75,0:16:27.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.75,0:16:34.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准對我家的上校——
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.71,0:16:40.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,——出手啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.27,0:16:44.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕特里克！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.17,0:16:48.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你  卡蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.90,0:16:55.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕特里克！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.32,0:16:58.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.27,0:16:59.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是艦船用船塢的入口！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.69,0:17:02.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用TRANS-AM一口氣加速！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.61,0:17:03.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突擊進去！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.23,0:17:11.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將GN-Field在艦首集中展開！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.53,0:17:27.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密成功著陸！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.87,0:17:32.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Archer-Arios  進行托勒密的防衛！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.44,0:17:36.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始掃描敵人母艦  尋找吠陀！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.74,0:17:37.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.62,0:17:39.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去0 Gundam那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.33,0:17:43.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依照戰術安排  我們分散開侵入敵人母艦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.48,0:17:44.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.49,0:17:45.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.27,0:17:56.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使入侵到內部  以MS短兵相接也要奪回吠陀嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.52,0:17:58.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.69,0:18:03.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大量自動機器人過來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.97,0:18:06.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有MS！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.81,0:18:09.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關閉所有隔離壁！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.57,0:18:11.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉塞  伊恩  準備應戰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.60,0:18:17.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備入侵！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.65,0:18:24.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想得逞  Gundam！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.95,0:18:28.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那機體是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.79,0:18:32.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易絲！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.76,0:18:46.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那機體…就是它將哥哥…！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.20,0:18:48.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧！ Fang！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.09,0:18:50.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈羅！ 啟動浮游步槍！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.09,0:18:50.50,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（RifleBit：與之前的ShieldBit不同，是以步槍為單位的浮游附屬裝置）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.71,0:18:51.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解  瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.09,0:19:05.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼窄的地方  你們也用不了TRANS-AM！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.61,0:19:11.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自動機器人突破了隔離壁  侵入本艦了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.89,0:19:12.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.89,0:19:13.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到吠陀了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.08,0:19:16.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將位置傳送給Meister！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.78,0:19:17.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得好  菲露特！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.62,0:19:21.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壓軸的上場了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.99,0:19:23.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再讓你前進了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.53,0:19:24.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別來礙事！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.87,0:19:25.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧  李維夫！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.13,0:19:26.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.04,0:19:28.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.81,0:19:34.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.35,0:19:39.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.33,0:19:54.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然戰爭就是要短兵相接才行啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.64,0:19:56.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口出狂言！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.92,0:20:03.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就再殺你一次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.07,0:20:05.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  開Gundam的！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.60,0:20:07.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滅了你！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.30,0:20:11.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.80,0:20:20.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩餘粒子量不多了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.49,0:20:21.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗  對接吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.10,0:20:25.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.16,0:20:32.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.32,0:20:36.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通向艦橋的隔離壁被打破了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.82,0:20:38.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.87,0:20:43.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特  米蕾娜  按照戰術進行應對
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.78,0:20:44.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.72,0:20:45.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.54,0:20:50.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要守住  這一次！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.93,0:21:01.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比利！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.81,0:21:03.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九條…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.88,0:21:13.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.21,0:21:22.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此強勁！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.72,0:21:24.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧  Fang！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.89,0:21:38.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是擾亂世界的罪惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.15,0:21:42.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要沒有了你們！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.36,0:21:43.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能幸福嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.62,0:21:44.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.86,0:21:49.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不斷戰鬥而贏得的未來  並不是真正的未來！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.23,0:21:56.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我們相互理解  才能築起未來！
